If you are in the United States and need suicide or mental health-related crisis support, or are worried about someone else, please call or text 988. Your call will be directed to a local mental health crisis center.

If you are located internationally, please visit findahelpline.com for a global list of helplines, hotlines, and crisis lines that can support you.

The Rare Impact Fund is part of our commitment to making a difference in the world – we're committed to raising awareness and increasing access to mental health services for young people.

This is needed now more than ever and we know we can’t do it alone. 

This World Mental Health Day, October 10th, @sephora is donating 100% of Rare Beauty sales to the Rare Impact Fund for 24 hours only.

Save the date and join us for 24 hours only on October 10th by shopping Rare Beauty at Sephora, online or in-store.

#RareImpact #MakeARareImpact

👏🏻👏🏼👏🏽👏🏾👏🏿 Too many people feel trapped by unrealistic expectations that are impossible to achieve. It’s about accepting who you are – and finding the beauty in your imperfections.

Here’s your reminder that you are welcome here and you are always enough, regardless of age, race, or gender.

This is a safe space, and supporting one another means the world to us. Your words matter (both to others and to yourself). Please join us in making social media a kinder place and compliment the person who commented before you below. 🫶
